snippet.title: Weekend Update: Get in the Cage with Nicolas Cage and Nicolas Cage - SNL
snippet.description:
Nicolas Cage gets in the cage with Nicolas Cage (Andy Samberg) to show they've sort of perfected cloning so he can star in every movie ever made and explain the keys to a good Nicolas Cage action movie. [Season 37, 2012]
